"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?23/11/23733/abstract/9\">",
"      Frishberg Y, Feinstein S, Drukker A. Living unrelated (commercial) renal transplantation in children. J Am Soc Nephrol 1998; 9:1100.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
