"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Peripheral blood smear from a patient with the \"Waring blender\" syndrome due to defective prosthetic heart valve. The smear shows marked red cell fragmentation with multiple sharp edges and small fragmented cells.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
